Even though he was born a normal man, in a normal body Robert Reynolds can't help but think he used to be something SUPER. The trouble is he can't seem to get anyone to believe him. He is also constantly hearing a dark brooding voice whispering evil things in his ear. Can Robert solve this SUPER mystery before the evil inside can destroy the entire world or is all of this just a dream? Welcome to Sentry the 5 part mini-series written by Paul Jenkins. The story serves as equal parts dejavu and nostalgia and is a roller coaster of a tale about a man who can't shake the feeling that he used to be a superhero!  If you can, please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

